            <summary>Manuscript is used for consultation by a priest or householder and contains rules, regulations, and proceedures for worshiping Hindu deities. There is a section honoring gurus (teachers) and one that praises the food offerings (prasāda) made to Śiva.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
